<recipe>
<title>
Fresh Herb Dip
</title>
<details>
AUTHOR: I Heart Eating
PREP TIME: 5 minutes
TOTAL TIME: 5 minutes
COURSE: Appetizer
CUISINE: American
SERVINGS: 10 servings
</details>
<ingredients><ingredient amount="0.75 Cup">Cheese</ingredient><ingredient amount="0.5 Cup">Mayonnaise</ingredient><ingredient amount="0.25 Cup">Yogurt</ingredient><ingredient amount="1.0 Tablespoon">Onion</ingredient><ingredient amount="2.0">Garlic</ingredient></ingredients>
<instructions>
Mix cottage cheese, mayonnaise, and Greek yogurt together.
Stir in parsley, dill or chives, onion, garlic, Worchestershire sauce, and salt.
Cover, and chill until ready to serve.
</instructions>
<cuisine>American</cuisine></recipe>